      "content": "i know i should talk to someone i guess but what's the point? it's not like talking about it changes the reality of it. i feel like i'm just playing a part every single day pretending to be someone i'm not, and honestly it's just too much to keep up. the world isn't built for people like me. it feels like there's just no way to win.",
